@startuml class-shell-domain
title App Shell Domain — Type Diagram

class Tab {
  +id: string
  +label: string
  +iconName: string
  +route: string
  +requiresAuth: boolean
}

class AgeBandTheme {
  +colors: ThemeColors
  +fontSizes: FontSizes
  +illustrations: string
}

class ThemeColors {
  +primary: string
  +secondary: string
  +accent: string
  +background: string
}

class FontSizes {
  +heading: string
  +body: string
  +caption: string
}

class NavigationState {
  +activeTab: string
  +activeProfile: Profile | null
  +isOnline: boolean
  +screenTimeRemaining: number | null
}

class PWAConfig {
  +name: string
  +shortName: string
  +display: "standalone"
  +themeColor: string
  +backgroundColor: string
  +icons: Icon[]
}

AgeBandTheme --> ThemeColors : colors
AgeBandTheme --> FontSizes : fontSizes
NavigationState --> Tab : activeTab references
NavigationState --> AgeBandTheme : resolved from profile

note bottom of AgeBandTheme
  Three predefined themes:
  - Seedlings (0-3): soft pastels
  - Sprouts (4-6): bright primary
  - Explorers (7-9): adventurous
end note

@enduml
